title: Great Community, Yards Available!
posting_body: ['Listing #2025', 'This community boasts a boutique-style setting that allows you to live effortlessly, with intentional designs.', 'These gorgeous one-, two, and three bedroom apartment homes are sure to delight!', 'From easy access to Downtown Austin, to the hundreds of miles of pristine shoreline at Lake Travis, this community is ideally situated for urban adventures of every kind.', "Visit today, and start experiencing true luxury, in harmony with Austin's extraordinary hospitality!", 'Community Amenities', 'Resident Clubhouse with Serving Kitchen and Billiards Table', 'Business Lounge with Private Conference Rooms', 'Resort Style Pool with Sunning Ledge, Cabanas and Expansive Deck with Gas Grills', 'Hammock Lawn and Outdoor Fire Place for Relaxation', 'Equipment, Free Weights and Spin Room with Interactive Classes', 'Package Acceptance with 24-7 Parcel Locker', 'Wi-Fi in All Common Areas', 'Tuck Under Garages', 'Covered Parking', 'Controlled Access Community', 'Valet Trash Service and Onsite Recycling', 'Pet Friendly Community with Pet Park', 'Rental Furniture Available From CORT', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Modern Urban Residences Featuring One and Two Bedrooms', 'Wood-Style Flooring in Living, Dining and Bath Areas', 'Custom Carpet in Bedrooms', 'Expansive 9’ Ceilings and Designer Inspired Accent Wall', 'Contemporary Lighting and Ceiling Fans', 'Full-Size Washer/Dryer Connections*', 'Washer/Dryers included*', '2” Blinds', 'Spacious Walk-In Closets with Custom Wood Shelving', 'Private Patio or Balconies', 'Includes Private Yards*', 'Includes Large Private Yards*', 'Call today to schedule your free tour!', 'I have access to over 1000 apartment listing in all areas in and around the beautiful Austin, Texas!', 'Should this listing not fit exactly what you are looking for, I am happy to help you find your next home!', 'Matt Davidson - Licensed Agent', 'Dash Apartment Locating', 'Dash Realty', 'show contact info', 'Listing #2025']
